messageBody:
Hello,

This email message is a notification to let you know that
a file has been uploaded to the Files area of the Read_Alphabet
group.

File : /International Quikscript/Malt's International Quikscript Project/adverbs__non_derived.ods
Uploaded by : peter_r_guinness <bacedif@...>
Description : Adverbs-non-derived Spreadsheet- lists pronunciation and QS spellings for common adverbs that are not derived by adding an 'ly' ending. Saved in ODF file format- use OpenOffice to view.

You can access this file at the URL:
http://groups.yahoo.com/group/Read_Alphabet/files/International%20Quikscript/Malt%27s%20International%20Quikscript%20Project/adverbs__non_derived.ods

To learn more about file sharing for your group, please visit:
http://help.yahoo.com/l/us/yahoo/groups/original/members/web/index.htmlfiles

Regards,

peter_r_guinness <bacedif@...>
